OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine and dry
OL,6,Finto the evening but thickening cloud
OL,7,Fand strengthening winds overnight will
OL,8,Fbring patchy outbreaks of rain to all
OL,9,Fareas by the early hours. Chilly, but
OL,10,Fa frost unlikely away from sheltered
OL,11,Frural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain continuing
OL,14,Finto the afternoon with winds easing
OL,15,Fsteadily. Brighter to end the day
OL,16,Falthough isolated showers remain
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
